<html>
<head>
	<meta charset='UTF-8'>
	<title></title>
</head>
<style type='text/css'>
	*, *:before, *:after { box-sizing: border-box; outline: none; }
	html, body { height: 100%; }
	body { background-color: #F5F5F5; font-size: 12px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: '微软雅黑', arial, sans-serif; }
	body, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, hr, p, blockquote, dl, dt, dd, ul, ol, li, pre, form, fieldset, legend, button, input, textarea, th, td, iframe { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
	img, article, aside, details, figcaption, figure, footer, header, menu, nav, section, summary, time, mark, audio, video { display: block; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
	h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 { font-size: 100%; }
	fieldset, img { border: 0; }
	address, caption, cite, dfn, em, th, var, i, em { font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; }
	ol, ul { list-style: none; }
	a { text-decoration: none;  }
	a:hover { text-decoration: none; }
	a, label, button, input, select { -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); }
	.contlist{width: 800px; margin:0 auto;}
	.contlist_ct{display: inline-block; width: 100%; background: #fff; 
	-webkit-box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
	-moz-box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
	box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
	margin-top: 20px;
	margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.imglist{display: inline-block; width: 100%; height: 114px;}
.imglist img{width: auto;height: auto;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;}
.contlist_ct_txt{width: 720px; margin:0 auto;}
.ft_center{padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px;}
</style>
<body>
	<div class='contlist'>
		<div class='contlist_ct'>
			<div class='imglist'>
				<img src='$image' style='width:800px;height:120px'/>
			</div>
			<div class='contlist_ct_txt'>
				<div class='v_warp '>
				<h3 style='text-align: center;    font-size: 18px; margin: 20px 0 20px; font-weight: normal;'>$report_type</h3>
				<div><strong>尊敬的 $user_name ,</strong></div>
				<div style='margin-bottom: 18px;line-height: 1.5rem;'>感谢您参加即将在 $address 召开的 $convention_name会议。以下为您被接受的摘要信息：</div>
				<p style='line-height: 1.5rem;'><strong>摘要编号: </strong> $TYPE<br>
				<strong>标题:</strong> $title<br>
				<strong>接受形式:</strong> $special<br>
				<strong>评审结果：</strong>$abstract_status</p>
	
				<p style='margin-top: 40px;'>&nbsp;</p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 20px;'>您可以将以上被录用的摘要制作成壁报在会议举办期间展示，为了您更好的同其他参会者交流，本次会议采用传统壁报的形式，您需要自行制作壁报携带到会场（上海国际会议中心五层公共区域），以下是制作壁报的尺寸：竖版宽90cm*高119cm（请参考下图），随着会期的临近，我们诚挚的盼望您能出席参加本次会议。</p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 100%; height: 428px;'>
				<img src='http://forum.sific.vip/uploads/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%872.png' style='width: auto;height: auto;max-width: 100%;max-height: 100%;'></p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-top: 20px;'>
				<a href='http://www.ajxd.com/' target='_blank'><img src='http://forum.sific.vip/uploads/%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%873.png' style='width: 229px; height: 100px; float:right;'></a>如果您确认参会并展示您的壁报，请您回复确认函至abstract@sific.org.cn</p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>&nbsp;</p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>若您的论文亦被评为口头报告形式，我们会再次与您联系！</span></p>
	
				<p style='color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 19.2px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>&nbsp;</p>
				<p>如有任何疑问，请随时与大会秘书处联系！</p>
				<p style='line-height: 1.5rem;'>感谢您对 $year 会议的大力支持！</p>
				<p> $year 摘要秘书处</p>
	
				<div style='padding-top: 20px;'>
				<div style='padding-top: 20px;'>
				<hr size='1' style='margin: 10px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(153, 153, 153); border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: dashed;'>
				<div id='foot'>
				<div class='ft_center'>
				<p align='center' style='line-height: 1.5rem;'><strong style='color: #666;'>$top</strong><br>
				邮箱: <a href='mailto:$email<' style='color: #;'>$email</a><strong><u> </u></strong></p>
	
				<p align='center'>电话：$tel </p>
				</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				</div>
				<div style='padding: 5px 15px 0px 5px; text-align: right; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-top-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; line-height: 45px;'>这是系统回执邮件,请不要回复!</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>